        <p>If you do not set the slideshow to loop, it will end at the final slide. This means that in the output, you cannot click the right navigation arrow to continue and start over with the first slide. Or if you have auto play settings enabled, the slideshow will not automatically continue after the last slide is shown.</p>
        <p>However, you can enable looping in the slideshow so that it will start over with the first slide. To do this, open the Edit Slideshow dialog. Select the <span class="Emphasis">Playback</span> tab, and select <span class="Emphasis">Loop</span>.</p>
